Absolute XPath, Relative XPath

web elementlerin'de testte kullanmak için attribute'lar;

-id,class,type,text
-css selector
-xpath

bu hiyerarşi'de kullanılır, xpath 2 ms sonra çalışır çünkü!

Absolute XPath:
/html/body/div[2]/div/section/figure/figcaption/div[2]

Relative XPath:
//*[@id='contact_form']
//div[text()='Sipariş']

Basic format for relative xpath:
//tagname[@attribute='value']

Contains():
XPath=//*[contains(@id,'nav')] --> id'lerin içerisinde nav geçen web elementleri arayıp bulmamı sağlar!
XPath=//*[contains(@type,'sub')] --> Every tags which contains 'sub' in type
XPath=//*[contains(@name,'btn')] --> Every tags which contains 'btn' in name
XPath=//*[contains(@id,'message')] --> Every tags which contains 'message' in id
XPath=//*[contains(@href,'guru99.com')] --> Every tags which contains 'guru99.com' in href
XPath=//h2[contains(@text(),'Popular right now')] --> Every h2 tags which contains 'Popular right now' in visible text

starts-with
XPath=//*[starts-with(@id,'message')] --> id'si message ile başlayanları verir!

Ends-with
XPath=//*[ends-with(@id,'message')] --> id'si message ile bitenleri verir!

using Or & And

XPath=//*[@type='submit' and @name='button'] --> tüm tagler içerisinde type'ı submit, name'i button olan web elementini bulur!
XPath=//button[@type'submit' or @name='button'] --> button tagleri içerisinde type'ı submit ya da name'i button olan web elementini bulur!

Text():
XPath=//*[text()='Watch the Videos']
XPath=//*[contains(text()),'Watch')]

Child:
XPath=//div[@id='main-navbar']//child::li

Siblings:
XPath=//*[@id='navBarDropdown']//following-sibling::div


